fields.name: Raisins
fields.description: Red raisins which are a nutritious and delicious snack, great for adding to your breakfast or baking! These raisins are ripened to the top natural sweetness level to ensure their flavour is kept

fields.name: Apricots
fields.description: Dried apricots are an excellent source of several important nutrients. Dried apricots provide a natural source of Iron, are high in fibre and low in fat

fields.name: Prunes
fields.description: Prunes are a healthy and nutritious snack option that is packed with essential vitamins, antioxidants, and fibre. They are perfect for anyone who wants to maintain a healthy lifestyle and is looking for a snack that is low in calories, fat-free, and gluten-free.

fields.name: Dried Apple
fields.description: Apples are an excellent source of fibre, vitamins and minerals. These dried rings are a perfect addition to any breakfast. They work especially well as a topper for porridge.

fields.name: Dried Banana
fields.description: Banana Chips are a great source of minerals, fibre & potassium. Banana Chips are the perfect healthy snack, delicious and with a  sweet & crunchy taste

fields.name: Goji Berries
fields.description: Considered one of the healthiest berries in the world, this superfood has many nutritional benefits as well as their delicious, sweet flavour. Packed with Iron, Vitamin A, Vitamin C, Calcium, Zinc, Potassium, Phosphorous, and various Antioxidants

fields.name: Chocolate peanuts
fields.description: High quality nuts, a delicious and crunchy treat, coated in luxury chocolate. Perfect for snacking or parties

fields.name: Chocolate raisins
fields.description: Milk Chocolate covered Raisins encased in smooth milk chocolate. Raisins are an excellent source of fibre, antioxidants, potassium, calcium and some B vitamins.

fields.name: Dark Chocoate Goldenberries
fields.description: Delicious and high in fibre. Goldenberries, dark chocolate, cacao powder. Potassium contributes to normal muscle function and normal function of the nervous system. Iron contributes to the reduction of tiredness and fatigue.

fields.name: Yoghurt coated raisins
fields.description: Wholesome, fruity juicy raisins dipped in a tasty yogurt flavour coating. Great as a snack on the go.

fields.name: Cashew Nuts
fields.description: Cashew nuts are a great source of manganese, potassium, copper, iron, magnesium, zinc and selenium. Or try delicious Roasted Cashews for snacking or adding to curries.

fields.name: Almonds
fields.description: Crunchy and delicious,Almonds are a highly nutritious tree nut rich in antioxidants, healthy fats, vitamins and minerals â€“ a sweet treat with a difference.

fields.name: Brazil Nuts
fields.description: Perfect to have as a delicious snack with health benefits! Thiamin contributes to the normal function of the heart. Selenium contributes to the maintenance of normal hair.

fields.name: Pistachio Nuts
fields.description: Pistachio Nutsstill in their shells to maintain their freshness and all natural nutty flavour.Magnesium contributes to the maintenance of normal bones. Thiamin contributes to the normal function of the heart.

fields.name: Sunflower seeds
fields.description: Sunflower seeds are a great natural source of vitamin E, which help to protect the body from oxidative damage caused by free radicals. They also contain a good amount of Zinc, Iron and Thiamin. .

fields.name: Tropical mix
fields.description: A delicious medley of chunky tropical fruit pieces, contains Raisins, Bananas, and Apricots.

fields.name: Goji Mix
fields.description: A delicious medley of chunky tropical fruit pieces, contains Goji Berries, Cashew Nuts, Brazil Nuts and Chocolate goldenberries.

fields.name: Mixed Roasted Nuts
fields.description: A delicious selection of roasted nut pieces, contains Almonds, Cashew Nuts and Peanuts.
